## License for Other Content

All other content on Enlighter, apart from the text, is licensed under [CC BY-NC-ND 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/).

You may distribute it in any form as long as you do not modify it, retain the link to **Enlighter**, credit our designers, and do not charge money for your product.

## Special Rules

Enlighter may occasionally include materials that are in the public domain or distributed under different licenses. In such cases, we will clearly indicate this on the page where the material is used, and publish the full license texts in our repositories.

If any of these licenses grant Enlighter exclusive rights to use specific assets, we kindly ask you not to reuse them in your own projects. However, we aim to keep Enlighter as open and accessible as possible.